                  Committee on Education and the Workforce

              Handicapped symbol   Web Site Accessibility Notice

                The Committee on Education and the Workforce is aware of
      and is making every attempt to comply with Section 508 of the
      Rehabilitation Act Amendments of 1998, as amended by Section 408 of
      the Workforce Investment Act of 1998.  If you have suggestions,
      comments or improvements for facilitating the Committees Web site
      presentation, or if you have difficulty accessing any page with
      adaptive technology, be sure to contact the Committee Webmaster.
      Please be as specific as possible in your description as well as
      including the location on the Committee Web site you are
      referencing.
